      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation experiments conducted on the same FDA generic pump geometry at VAD operating conditions; fluid is human blood or equivalent analogue with documented equivalency.",
      "rationale": "Validation experiments used a glycerol-water analogue rather than blood, and operating conditions cover only 3 of the 5 required flow-speed combinations. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
    },
