      "acceptanceCriteria": "Independent analyst replication of simulation setup and post-processing; documented checklist for model configuration reviewed by a second qualified engineer.",
      "rationale": "No independent replication or analyst cross-check has been performed. Use error is a known epistemic gap at MRL 5 for this assessment."
    },
    {
