      "factorType": "Model form",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 5,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Systematic evaluation of turbulence closure and hemolysis constitutive model form uncertainty; alternative model forms compared against experimental data at VAD conditions.",
      "rationale": "Model form uncertainty for both the turbulence closure (SST k-omega) and the power-law hemolysis model has not been systematically evaluated. No alternative model forms were tested. Critical epistemic gap at MRL 5."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model inputs",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 5,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
