      "acceptanceCriteria": "Full Monte Carlo propagation of input parameter uncertainties (material properties, boundary conditions, geometric tolerances) through hemolysis QoI with documented probability distributions.",
      "rationale": "Although Monte Carlo UQ is referenced in the COU description, the input probability distributions for material constants in the hemolysis model have not been formally documented or peer-reviewed. Assessment incomplete."
    },
