      "factorType": "Test samples",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Minimum three independent pump specimens tested; inter-specimen variability characterised and propagated into validation uncertainty budget.",
      "rationale": "Experimental data derives from a single pump specimen. Inter-specimen variability has not been characterised. This represents a significant epistemic gap for a Class III device at MRL 5."
